details: Enhance your nails with Gel X extensions—flexible, long-lasting, and designed for a flawless natural finish.
Après Gel X is the modern alternative to acrylics—soft gel tips cured under LED light for elegant, flexible, and long-lasting nails.
Achieve beautiful, long-lasting nails with builder gel—designed to add strength, structure, and natural elegance.
A rejuvenating builder gel fill to restore, strengthen, and seamlessly refresh your existing set.
